{"id":4204,"date":"2025-06-16T14:17:38","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T07:17:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4204"},"modified":"2025-06-16T14:19:21","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T07:19:21","slug":"kem-chong-nang-vat-ly","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/kem-chong-nang-vat-ly\/","title":{"rendered":"Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd &#8211; L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn an to\u00e0n cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch? Trong s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n nay, <\/span><\/i><b><i>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 lo\u1ea1i kem n\u00e0y: t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1eb9o d\u00f9ng sao cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kem-chong-nang-vat-ly-la-sao\"><\/span><b>Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd l\u00e0 sao?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp m\u00e0n ch\u1eafn kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t tr\u00ean da, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00ean g\u1ecdi \u201csunblock\u201d. C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu l\u1ea1i tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00fang ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec. C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 titanium dioxide v\u00e0 zinc oxide &#8211; nh\u1eefng kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u00edt g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4205\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4205\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4205\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-1.webp\" alt=\"Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd l\u00e0 sao\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4205\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd l\u00e0 sao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong-cua-kem-chong-nang-vat-ly\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay v\u00ec th\u1ea5m v\u00e0o da nh\u01b0 d\u00f2ng h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, lo\u1ea1i kem n\u00e0y b\u00e1m tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tia UV. N\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp \u00e1o kho\u00e1ng m\u1ecfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a tia t\u1eed ngo\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 UVA v\u00e0 UVB. V\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o da n\u00ean nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u1ea3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-diem-va-nhuoc-diem-can-can-nhac\"><\/span><b>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uu-diem-noi-bat\"><\/span><b><i>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ngay sau khi thoa m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 hai lo\u1ea1i tia UVA v\u00e0 UVB.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cao, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"han-che-can-luu-y\"><\/span><b><i>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c n\u1eb7ng m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7n thoa l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng, g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da ng\u0103m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f3 h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, g\u00e2y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng &#8220;cakey&#8221; n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hai-thanh-phan-chu-chot-trong-kem-chong-nang-vat-ly\"><\/span><b>Hai th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Zinc Oxide (K\u1ebdm Oxit)<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> C\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3 UVA v\u00e0 UVB. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn an to\u00e0n khi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn 25%.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Titanium Dioxide (Titan Dioxit)<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tia UVB v\u00e0 UVA b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng ng\u1eafn. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u1edbp tr\u1eafng nh\u1eb9, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nano c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1edbn v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean 6 th\u00e1ng tu\u1ed5i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4206\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4206\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4206\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-2.webp\" alt=\"Hai th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4206\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hai th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 GRASE (Generally Recognized As Safe and Effective), t\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-su-dung-dung-cach-de-toi-uu-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4207\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4207\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4207\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-3.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/70-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4207\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00f4i kem v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da, sau l\u1edbp d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc trang \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00ean \u0111\u1ee3i 10\u201315 ph\u00fat sau khi d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thoa kem.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean v\u00f9ng c\u1ed5, tai v\u00e0 sau g\u00e1y \u2013 nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed7i 2 ti\u1ebfng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ra ngo\u00e0i, v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 trong nh\u00e0 hay ng\u00e0y \u00e2m u, h\u00e3y duy tr\u00ec th\u00f3i quen ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n v\u00ec tia UV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean qua k\u00ednh v\u00e0 m\u00e2y m\u00f9.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"goi-y-vi-sao-nen-thu-gsc-triple-sun-block\"><\/span><b>G\u1ee3i \u00fd: V\u00ec sao n\u00ean th\u1eed GSC Triple Sun Block?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Triple Sun Block l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t l\u00e0 titanium dioxide, zinc oxide, c\u00f9ng niacinamide v\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 m\u1eabu \u0111\u01a1n, cam th\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed3i &#8211; s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da m\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng, ng\u1eeba k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nh\u1eddn d\u00ednh kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4201\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4201\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4201\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1.webp\" alt=\"GSC Triple Sun Block\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/69-5-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4201\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Triple Sun Block<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc. V\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng, d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1edbp l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn an to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da m\u1ecfng manh. H\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00ecn gi\u1eef v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng d\u00e0i l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch? Trong s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n nay, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4208,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4204","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4204","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4204"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4204\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4209,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4204\/revisions\/4209"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"e